        "prompt": "Create a tri-fold travel brochure for a 4-day, 3-night 杭州 self-guided itinerary, with a real 杭州 map as the central spine, landmark illustrations floating on cardstock.\n\nStyle/medium: needs a travel-attack-card / illustrated-brochure aesthetic — exact stylistic execution is yours\nComposition: must be tri-fold layout with real 杭州 map as central spine, 4 day-panels divided clearly, landmark icons floating above cardstock with drop shadows\nSubject: must include all scenic spots, dining, tips, and accommodation across 4 day-panels:\n  Day 1 (西湖经典游): 断桥残雪 / 白堤 / 孤山 / 曲院风荷 / 苏堤春晓 / 花港观鱼 / 雷峰塔 / 柳浪闻莺\n  Day 2 (禅意杭州): 灵隐寺 / 飞来峰 / 法喜寺 / 宋城\n  Day 3 (九溪烟树): 九溪十八涧 / 龙井村 / 十里琅珰 / 云栖竹径\n  Day 4A (运河文艺线): 拱宸桥 / 桥西历史街区 / 小河直街 / 大兜路香积寺\n  Day 4B (西溪湿地): 周家村 / 深潭口 / 西溪湿地氦气球\nScene/backdrop: must be a real 杭州 map base with all routes visually connecting day-panels; landmark illustrations must float above a cardstock surface with visible shadow\nLighting/mood: needs a warm, inviting travel-guide atmosphere — exact light treatment is yours\nColor palette: needs a direction evoking 江南 ink-wash meets modern travel-card vibrancy — exact palette and ratios are yours\nMaterials/textures: must include paper cardstock surface with floating shadow under each landmark cutout\nText (verbatim): must include the following itinerary copy verbatim across panels —\n  Day 1: \"西湖经典游，打卡教科书里的江南\" | 路线：断桥残雪→白堤→孤山→曲院风荷→苏堤春晓→花港观鱼→雷峰塔→柳浪闻莺 | ⏰ 7:30出发 | 午餐：楼外楼（东坡肉+龙井虾仁，人均150元）| ⚠️ 租共享单车（每小时5元）\n  Day 2: \"禅意杭州，穿越千年宋韵\" | 路线：灵隐寺→飞来峰造像→法喜寺→宋城 | 灵隐寺十八籽手串（46元）| 《宋城千古情》贵宾席（320元）| 晚餐：素描餐厅（人均90元）\n  Day 3: \"九溪烟树徒步，做一日茶山散人\" | 路线：九溪十八涧→龙井村→十里琅珰→云栖竹径 | 龙井问茶（50元/杯）| 摆渡车（8元）| 晚餐：茶人村（人均120元）\n  Day 4A: \"运河文艺线\" | 拱宸桥→桥西历史街区→小河直街→大兜路香积寺 | 中国伞/刀剪剑博物馆（免费）| 水上巴士1号线（3元）\n  Day 4B: \"西溪湿地轻奢游\" | 周家村→深潭口→氦气球俯瞰湿地（180元）\n  伴手礼：南宋胡记荷花酥（38元/盒）/ 万事利丝绸方巾（150-300元）\n  住宿：✅ 杭州君悦酒店 / 青芝坞民宿（人均200元）| ❌ 避雷：火车站周边\n  交通：地铁支付宝\"杭州地铁乘车码\" | 萧山机场→西湖：地铁1号线（7元/50分钟）| 灵隐寺专线：龙翔桥乘7W路（5元）\nConstraints: must preserve real geographic accuracy of 杭州 map; all 4 day-panels must be visible in tri-fold layout; all 景点、餐厅、交通、住宿条目必须完整保留\nAvoid: ",
